fastfetch

%VERSION%
2.20.0-1

%BASE%
fastfetch

%DESC%
Like Neofetch, but much faster because written in C

%URL%
https://github.com/fastfetch-cli/fastfetch

%ARCH%
x86_64

%BUILDDATE%
1721976611

%INSTALLDATE%
1722007834

